Your dad owns this place now,

11:42.494 --> 11:44.872
but I still have to make surehe's managing the place.

11:44.955 --> 11:46.248
Keep telling yourself that,

11:46.331 --> 11:49.960
but the real reason you come hereis to flirt with the young girls.

11:50.043 --> 11:51.795
-[grunts]-I see right through you.

11:51.879 --> 11:52.963
-[chuckles]-[Goto laughs]

11:53.755 --> 11:55.174
Ah, Hirota!

11:57.092 --> 11:58.802
This is my son, Solomon.

11:58.886 --> 12:00.888
[Hirota grunts] You finally came home. [Hirota grunts] You finally came home.

12:00.971 --> 12:03.140
