12:29.541 --> 12:32.294
A man who is dead and gone.

12:32.878 --> 12:34.671
Nothing to do with us.

12:37.841 --> 12:41.386
-[machine balls clatter]-Jackpot! [giggles, gasps]

12:41.470 --> 12:42.679
Look at that!

12:42.763 --> 12:45.224
