12:52.147 --> 12:54.149
[boat horn blows]

13:10.165 --> 13:11.792
[people in market chattering]

13:12.459 --> 13:13.669
Ooh.

13:14.586 --> 13:16.046
[laughs]

13:31.144 --> 13:32.312
[whistle blows]

13:34.773 --> 13:36.733
-[chattering fades]-[footsteps approaching]

13:41.113 --> 13:42.155
Sunja.

13:42.239 --> 13:44.658
Sunja, head down.

