14:48.388 --> 14:49.389
Let's go.

14:50.516 --> 14:52.893
-Hey there!-[vendor] Oh.

14:53.477 --> 14:55.020
Isn't this one fine?

14:55.103 --> 14:58.732
I bet you can't show mea better catch, not today.

14:59.233 --> 15:00.984
It's huge. What can I do with it? It's huge. What can I do with it?

