Your fish cakes are the bestin the market, Mr. Kim.

15:04.363 --> 15:07.616
You always sell out of them before noon.

15:07.699 --> 15:09.493
But with this big guy right here,

15:09.576 --> 15:13.413
you can make enough fish cakesto last for weeks.

15:13.497 --> 15:15.874
In that case, I'll give you 30 for it, OK?

15:15.958 --> 15:17.918
