15:42.609 --> 15:44.027
That price is OK.

15:44.736 --> 15:45.779
[laughs]

15:47.656 --> 15:49.867
-[grunts]-Good. Many thanks.

15:50.409 --> 15:53.036
Here! Your share.

15:54.329 --> 15:55.330
Oh…

15:55.873 --> 15:57.541
I'm not allowed to take it.

15:57.624 --> 16:00.002
