16:31.491 --> 16:33.160
is this what they meant?

16:35.204 --> 16:36.205
Sunja.

16:37.122 --> 16:38.165
Should we go now?

16:39.750 --> 16:40.792
[fisherman] OK.

16:40.876 --> 16:43.879
See you back at the house. [chuckles]

16:48.133 --> 16:48.967
Papa.

16:50.469 --> 16:52.804
The man we saw in the market earlier…

16:53.639 --> 16:55.265
… did he do something bad?

16:56.099 --> 16:57.309
I don't know.

16:57.893 --> 16:59.311
Truth is, nowadays…

17:00.646 --> 17:04.358
… it's hard for us to judgebetween guilt or innocence.

17:06.902 --> 17:09.112
What will happen to him now?

17:09.988 --> 17:12.449
Will he be allowed to go home or not?

17:13.534 --> 17:14.535
Sunja.

17:16.328 --> 17:17.871
I once made a vow to you.

17:19.540 --> 17:21.791
When you were barely a week old…

17:22.376 --> 17:25.212
… your mother and Iwould stay up every night.

17:27.381 --> 17:30.217
All our days and nights,we watched over you.

17:31.718 --> 17:34.137
That's when I made you this solemn vow…

17:35.681 --> 17:38.559
… that as long as you drew breath,

17:38.642 --> 17:40.644
there's nothing I wouldn't do

17:40.727 --> 17:43.397
to ward off all the ugliness in this world

17:43.480 --> 17:45.023
and keep it far away from you.

17:47.150 --> 17:48.277
Mmm.

17:49.653 --> 17:52.573
