17:56.410 --> 17:57.411
[chuckles]

17:58.161 --> 17:59.705
[steam whistle blows]

18:02.749 --> 18:04.293
[steam whistle blows]

18:38.535 --> 18:39.745
[Solomon] Grandma!

19:12.069 --> 19:13.070
[chuckles]

19:31.004 --> 19:32.464
[clicks tongue, inhales]

19:32.548 --> 19:34.967
[playing simple tune]

19:43.225 --> 19:44.893
