21:04.431 --> 21:06.433
It's all the same when you're a woman.

21:07.059 --> 21:08.810
She must learn to feed herself.

21:12.189 --> 21:15.150
In the cove, the water is calm today.

21:15.234 --> 21:18.153
The woman will help mewith my lessons if I go.

21:18.779 --> 21:19.863
So can I go?

21:20.614 --> 21:22.032
Have you been listening or not?

21:22.699 --> 21:25.452
Mmm. Next time, I'll tell Mr. Song

21:25.536 --> 21:27.955
that I can't listen because I'm a girl.

21:28.705 --> 21:30.082
Never mind that--

21:30.165 --> 21:34.002
And because he's not much of a fisherman,he can't be giving me money.

21:34.086 --> 21:35.254
[sighs]

21:36.296 --> 21:37.756
Fine, on your way.

21:39.299 --> 21:40.717
[grunts]

21:41.593 --> 21:42.594
Listen.

21:42.678 --> 21:45.597
It's good that you love her,but you dote on her too much.

21:45.681 --> 21:46.515
[sighs]

21:46.598 --> 21:49.852
