21:53.105 --> 21:54.940
It wasn't your money to give!

21:55.023 --> 21:57.234
It was another's kindness.

21:58.235 --> 22:02.406
She needs to know there's such a thingas kindness in this world. She needs to know there's such a thingas kindness in this world.

22:03.657 --> 22:06.869
