22:11.915 --> 22:12.916
[sighs]

22:34.354 --> 22:36.190
Sunja!

22:37.566 --> 22:39.526
[Sunja] Watch me!

23:53.267 --> 23:54.601
[panting]

24:12.369 --> 24:13.412
Sunja!

24:13.495 --> 24:14.913
[breathes heavily]

24:16.707 --> 24:17.708
Sunja!

24:20.169 --> 24:21.587
[Sunja] Daddy!

24:23.797 --> 24:25.799
Look! I did it!

