-Can't take the ocean from us, can they?-Mmm.

25:56.139 --> 25:58.141
Don't talk like a stupid idiot.

25:58.976 --> 26:00.978
Huh? What are you saying? Huh? What are you saying?

26:01.728 --> 26:04.022
We just let them take our land.

26:04.857 --> 26:06.024
Didn't we?

